 420:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Function description
 421:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Stores a specified number of characters in SEGGER RTT ring buffer
 422:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    and updates the associated write pointer which is periodically
 423:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    read by the host.
