 553:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Function description
 554:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Reads characters from SEGGER real-time-terminal control block
 555:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    which have been previously stored by the application.
 556:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Do not lock against interrupts and multiple access.
 557:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Used to do the same operation that J-Link does, to transfer 
