 562:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    pBuffer      Pointer to buffer provided by target application, to copy characters from RTT-up-
 563:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    BufferSize   Size of the target application buffer.
 564:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
 565:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Return value
 566:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Number of bytes that have been read.
 567:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
 568:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Additional information
 569:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    This function must not be called when J-Link might also do RTT.
 570:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** */
