1694:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Function description
1695:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Run-time configuration of a specific down-buffer (H->T).
1696:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Buffer to be configured is specified by index.
1697:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    This includes: Buffer address, size, name, flags, ...
1698:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
1699:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Parameters
1700:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    BufferIndex  Index of the buffer to configure.
1701:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    sName        Pointer to a constant name string.
1702:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    pBuffer      Pointer to a buffer to be used.
1703:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    BufferSize   Size of the buffer.
1704:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Flags        Operating modes. Define behavior if buffer is full (not enough space for entire m
1705:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
1706:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Return value
1707:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    >= 0  O.K.
1708:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *     < 0  Error
1709:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
1710:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Additional information
1711:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Buffer 0 is configured on compile-time.
1712:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    May only be called once per buffer.
1713:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Buffer name and flags can be reconfigured using the appropriate functions.
1714:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** */
